      <div class="w-full md:w-1/5"></div>
      <div class="markdown w-full md:w-3/5">
        <h1>
          Preview Plugin
        </h1>
        <p>
          The preview plugin adds a new element <code>{{ "<plx-preview>" | escape }}</code>.
        </p>

        <div class="w-4/5 relative">
          <player-x loading="user" src="https://vimeo.com/357274789" controls>
            <plx-media></plx-media>
            <plx-preview loading="lazy" src="https://vimeo.com/357274789" oembed-url="{{ site.apiUrl }}/oembed"></plx-preview>
          </player-x>
        </div>

